Class DistributedBackend

java.lang.Object
  ibbt.sumo.sampleevaluators.distributed.DistributedBackend
Direct Known Subclasses:
RemoteDistributedBackend
public abstract class DistributedBackend
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a baseclass for all distributed resource backends. Such backends typically have their own SampleEvaluator.
